{"_path":"/fitness/f003","_dir":"fitness","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"腹部運動","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":3,"category":"室內運動","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-26T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"腹部運動"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"腹部運動"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"夏天就是秀出腹肌马甲线最好的时期了，接下来我讲介绍五个刺激腹部的有效动作，让你在家就可以练出完美的腹肌马甲线！\n五个动作各 20 次为一组，一次训练建议做 2 ～ 3 组，连续坚持 14 天，你会拥有马甲线的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第一个动作：仰卧左右交替体侧屈：双脚不要移动，卷起腹部，用双手左右去摸脚跟。一组 20 次\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f003-01.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f003-01.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二个动作：仰卧屈膝卷腹：双手扶地不要发力，要用腹部的力量去带动腿部向上。一组 20 次\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f003-02.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f003-02.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第三个动作：单腿两头起：尽量用手去摸脚，膝盖不要弯曲。一组 20 次\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f003-03.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f003-03.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第四个动作：俯卧登山：核心、肩膀及手臂要保持稳定，不随着髋关节的动作而摇晃，注意身体一直保持最自然的一直线，利用核心肌群，控制身体的稳定。一组 20 次\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f003-04.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f003-04.gif"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第五个动作：仰卧交替抬腿：下背部用力贴紧地面，双腿伸直，勾起脚尖，双腿交替在与地面呈 45° 角和 70° 角的区间内抬起落下。一组 20 次\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"f003-05.jpeg","src":"/images/fitness/f003-05.gif"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"腹部運動","depth":2,"text":"腹部運動"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:fitness:f003.md","_source":"content","_file":"fitness/f003.md","_extension":"md"}